subMembers.name: searchEnabled
subMembers.description: Specifies whether the search panel is visible.

subMembers.name: searchExpr
subMembers.description: Specifies a data object's field name or an expression whose value is compared to the search string.

subMembers.name: searchMode
subMembers.description: Specifies a comparison operation used to search UI component items.

subMembers.name: searchTimeout
subMembers.description: Specifies a delay in milliseconds between when a user finishes typing, and the search is executed.
